Hungary May Name Torocskei as Debt Chief, Privatbankar Reports

-- B y   E d i t h   B a l a z s
-- 
2011-10-21T13:34:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-21/hungary-may-name-torocskei-as-debt-chief-privatbankar-reports.html
Hungary may appoint Istvan Torocskei
as the new chief executive officer of the Debt Management
Agency, Privatbankar said, citing unidentified market sources.  Torocskei is an economist who began his career at the
central bank and later switched to private business, the news
portal said. He may replace Gyula Pleschinger, who will be named
state secretary at the  Economy Ministry  with oversight of the
debt agency, Privatbankar said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Edith Balazs in Budapest at 
 ebalazs1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Zoltan Simon at 
 zsimon@bloomberg.net  